---
<BaseLayout
  title={`Web Design ${city} MD | WordPress & SEO | Upcoming Brand`}
  description={`Web design ${city} businesses trust for real Google rankings. Custom WordPress builds, 90+ PageSpeed, fixed pricing. Serving Frederick City, Urbana, Middletown, and Frederick County.`}
  canonicalUrl={canonical}
>
  <!-- JSON-LD in head slot -->
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={jsonLd} />

  <AnnouncementBar />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <ServiceHero
    eyebrow='A studio, not a factory'
    pillText='WordPress Specialists · Frederick, MD'
    h1Lines={[
      { text: 'Frederick' },
      { text: 'web design that ranks,', type: 'accent' },
      { text: 'converts & keeps working.', type: 'italic' },
    ]}
    lead={`Upcoming Brand is a Maryland-based WordPress web design studio. We design and build custom WordPress websites for <strong>law firms, biotech companies, restaurants, real estate brokerages,</strong> and small businesses across Frederick City, Urbana, Middletown, and Frederick County - sites that rank in Google, convert visitors, and keep running long after launch day.`}
    formName='frederick-inquiry'
    trustLines={['Top Rated · Upwork', '400+ projects · 12 countries', 'Remote-first · Zoom · Async']}
    hiddenFields={{ location: 'Frederick, MD' }}
    formSteps={[
      {
        title: 'Tell us who you are',
        subtitle: 'Just your name and email. 30 seconds.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'text',  name: 'name',  label: 'Your name',     placeholder: 'Jane Smith',       required: true, autocomplete: 'name' },
          { type: 'email', name: 'email', label: 'Email address', placeholder: 'jane@company.com', required: true, autocomplete: 'email' },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'About your business',
        subtitle: 'Company and what you do.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'text', name: 'company', label: 'Company or brand', placeholder: 'Smith & Co.', autocomplete: 'organization' },
          { type: 'select', name: 'business_type', label: 'Business type', required: true,
            options: ['Law Firm / Attorney', 'Dental / Medical', 'Real Estate', 'Restaurant / Hospitality', 'Contractor / Trades', 'Nonprofit / Church', 'Ecommerce / Retail', 'Small Business / Startup', 'Other'] },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'What you need',
        subtitle: 'Which service and your budget.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'select', name: 'service_interest', label: 'Service interested in', required: true,
            options: ['New WordPress site build', 'Redesign existing site', 'WooCommerce store', 'WordPress SEO services', 'Migration to WordPress', 'Care plan / maintenance', 'SEO audit', 'Not sure yet'] },
          { type: 'select', name: 'budget', label: 'Budget range', required: true,
            options: ['Under $1,500', '$1,500 to $3,500', '$3,500 to $6,000', '$6,000 to $15,000', '$15,000+', 'Not sure yet'] },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'Timeline + goal',
        subtitle: 'When you need it and what success looks like.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'select', name: 'timeline', label: 'Timeline', required: true,
            options: ['ASAP, within 4 weeks', 'Standard, 6 to 10 weeks', 'Flexible, 3+ months', 'Just exploring'] },
          { type: 'textarea', name: 'message', label: 'Project goal', placeholder: 'Three sentences. We will ask the rest in the reply.', required: true, rows: 2 },
        ],
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       DEFINITION
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lp-definition section-pad-sm" aria-labelledby="def-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="lp-def-inner">

        <div class="lp-def-left">
          <span class="lp-def-label mono-xs">In plain English</span>
          <h2 class="lp-def-heading" id="def-heading">What is custom WordPress web design?</h2>
          <div class="lp-def-amber-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="lp-def-right">
          <p class="lp-def-body">Custom WordPress web design means building your site from a blank canvas on WordPress CMS - not installing a $59 theme already running on 40,000 other businesses. For a Frederick County law firm near the courthouse on North Court Street, that means intake forms, LegalService schema, and attorney biography pages that build trust before a potential client calls. For a Carroll Creek restaurant, it means a design built around seasonal menu photography and reservation flows that don't break on mobile. For a Fort Detrick-adjacent biotech company, it means MedicalOrganization schema, HIPAA-aware contact forms, and pages structured to rank for research and clinical search terms. You own the code outright with no monthly platform fee. Every build ships with 90+ PageSpeed, JSON-LD schema matched to your exact business type, and all three Core Web Vitals passing before the DNS transfers.</p>

          <div class="lp-def-facts">
            <div class="lp-def-fact">
              <span class="lp-def-fact-num">90<span class="lp-def-fact-sup">+</span></span>
              <span class="lp-def-fact-lbl mono-xs">PageSpeed on every build</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lp-def-fact">
              <span class="lp-def-fact-num">$0</span>
              <span class="lp-def-fact-lbl mono-xs">Platform fee after launch</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lp-def-fact">
              <span class="lp-def-fact-num">3</span>
              <span class="lp-def-fact-lbl mono-xs">Core Web Vitals in the green</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       LOCAL PROOF PILLARS
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lp-pillars section-pad-sm" aria-labelledby="pillars-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="lp-section-intro">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why local matters</p>
        <h2 class="h2-section" id="pillars-heading">What a {city}-based WordPress studio does differently</h2>
        <p class="lead">Most web design agencies are remote-only marketplaces that assign your project to whoever's available. We're a Maryland studio - remote-first by design, but built around the Frederick and Frederick County market. We know which corridors are growing fastest, which industries are competitive, and which search terms your customers run before they call anyone.</p>
      </div>

